<h2 id=3D"2">sqids 0.1.0</h2>
<div class=3D"outline-text-2" id=3D"text-2">
<p>
Archive: <a href=3D"https://discuss.ocaml.org/t/ann-sqids-0-1-0/14425/1">ht=
