<div id=3D"outline-container-org8738738" class=3D"outline-3">
<h3 id=3D"org8738738">Leo Soares announced</h3>
<div class=3D"outline-text-3" id=3D"text-org8738738">
<p>
I'm happy to announce the first release (0.1.0) of the <a href=3D"https://s=
qids.org/ocaml">official OCaml port of Sqids</a>.
</p>

<blockquote>
<p>
Sqids (pronounced "squids") is an open-source library that lets you generat=
e short unique identifiers from numbers. These IDs are
URL-safe, can encode several numbers, and do not contain common profanity w=
ords.
</p>
</blockquote>

<p>
<a href=3D"https://opam.ocaml.org/packages/sqids">https://opam.ocaml.org/pa=
ckages/sqids</a>
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
